{"tid":1695761,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來身邊大家都做緊野 分享挑戰！用IG救港","createTime":"2019-11-05T23:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T23:54:46.000Z","uid":24173,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8e74cb5b1cbc10892b82e318b95a83a25bb883","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">分享你為香港做過嘅野</span></span></strong><br />\n最近連登風氣比班3毛帶到分化哂 互相指責<br />\n喺手足指責同路人飲飲食食嘅時候，有無諗過手足其實係做左好多野，但你唔知<br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋成日講發夢嘅野唔好周圍講，唔好自爆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span></strong></span>  食黃店 做文宣 打網絡戰（e.g: Twitter)又怕咩講？<br />\n<br />\n請大家今日開始將做過嘅嘢貼上IG 可以@下同路人 朋友<br />\n邀請佢一齊 做野 。<br />\n<br />\n今日你痴 文宣 @完佢 跟住佢上Twitter 打完網絡戰 又tag其他人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好由得風氣比人帶 我地應該主動帶起風氣<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革面 請用IG （或者其他apps)帶起救港風氣"},{"pid":"81bdbf79039aab28d2113311f67495f80178f6cc","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:39:25.000Z","msg":"之前都有手足講過類似嘅野 希望可以真係做到"},{"pid":"66099ca8fe01794375e1829535bdfa526e3b6c9c","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"47d2a7cee7ffcef20f136fb056e59988d134dd25","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:40:04.000Z","msg":"老土d講句 用生命影響生命"},{"pid":"9a294cf07dd5331996df04f2f713e091188b008e","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:40:35.000Z","msg":"大家唔係講過 要形成黃色經濟圈咩"},{"pid":"67c9810678ad8299648678d960887d226b49b681","tid":1695761,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:40:57.000Z","msg":"自己食係唔夠 要影響身邊嘅人一齊食"},{"pid":"2ee4848db284f389c026c166bbf91c25ca0